-- Northern Malians Protest Enforcement of Shariah Law, Essor Says
-- B y   D i a k a r i d i a   D e m b e l e
-- 2012-06-07T11:32:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-07/northern-malians-protest-enforcement-of-shariah-law-essor-says.html
About 200 people held a protest in
the northern Malian city of Kidal to demonstrate against the
enforcement of Shariah law in the area, l’Essor reported.  The residents, mostly young people and women, gathered near
the city’s stadium, the state-owned newspaper, based in Bamako,
cited a resident as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Diakaridia Dembele in Bamako via Accra at 
